<br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">無線新聞立場偏頗、時常斷章取義，多年來誤導不少港人，懇請 貴公司轉用其他宣傳渠道，例如蘋果日報、ViuTV、77台，以免間接資助一間為中共維穩的電視台！而在 貴公司重新審視宣傳策略前，我及我的親朋戚友將會盡量避免光顧 貴公司，敬請注意。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n============================================<br />\n如果想準時收到TVB任務，一定要響Facebook同Telegram follow sayno4tvb團隊（我唔係佢地團隊），又或者<strong><span class=\"red\">得閒click入呢個Post（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2059659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2059659</a>）我會盡量每日更新</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=467b55a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno4tvb&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=707a1a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno4tvb</a><br />\n舊版抵制List: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/tvbadver\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftvbadver&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoAwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=11b42865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/tvbadver</a><br />\n<br />\n最後都要重申，<span class=\"red\">我地支持自由經濟，我地同意廣告商有賣廣告既自由，但顧客都有選擇買同唔買既自由</span>，我地只會抵制無良商戶，但唔會威脅佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVG4nk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVG4nk5.jpg&h=69dd4c04&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7yVHqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7yVHqJ.jpg&h=ececd494&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbYiswE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbYiswE.jpg&h=d3b9ed92&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5op